readme:
# Bonsoir Syntax Theme

With a dark interface, and subdued colors this theme is easy on the eyes.

## Screenshots

### HTML
![Bonsoir HTML Syntax](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RyleeHarrison/bonsoir-syntax/master/screenshots/screen-html.png)

### JavaScript
![Bonsoir JavaScript Syntax](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RyleeHarrison/bonsoir-syntax/master/screenshots/screen-js.png)

### CSS
![Bonsoir CSS Syntax](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RyleeHarrison/bonsoir-syntax/master/screenshots/screen-css.png)

### Bonus
![Bonsoir Bonus Syntax](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RyleeHarrison/bonsoir-syntax/master/screenshots/random/1.png)
![Bonsoir Bonus Syntax](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RyleeHarrison/bonsoir-syntax/master/screenshots/random/2.png)
![Bonsoir Bonus Syntax](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RyleeHarrison/bonsoir-syntax/master/screenshots/random/3.png)

## Install

```
apm install bonsoir-syntax
```
